collections.name: Japanese nude NFTs
collections.description:
JNN has no fixed roadmap. However, our goal is clear. JNN is focused on transforming the personal and physical information of all adult performers into NFTs, turning them into digital assets.

Through this, we aim to revolutionize the existing structure of the adult industry and create a safer and more transparent environment. By utilizing NFT technology, we can protect performers' rights while preventing illegal reproduction and unauthorized use. Additionally, it enables the establishment of a fair revenue distribution system.

JNN is not merely about adopting new technology; our mission is to fundamentally reshape the paradigm of the adult industry. By introducing a system that aligns with the digital era, we strive to build a future where both performers and users can engage with trust and confidence.

collections.name: NIGHT ANGEL
collections.description:
**🌑 Night Angel: Sole Collector Edition 🌌**

**Behold the *Night Angel: Sole Collector*** — a singular, transcendent incarnation of the cosmos’ most guarded secrets. Forged in the crucible of a supernova and bound by the oath of eternity, this one-of-a-kind NFT embodies the apex of celestial power and mystery. collections.name: CYBER WARRIORS
collections.description:
"Quantum Vanguard: The Cyber Warriors of the Shattered Codeverse"

**Prologue:**  
In the fractured expanse of the *Neural Nexus*, where data streams bleed corrupted code and quantum servers hum with forbidden algorithms, a legendary cadre of digital warriors emerged from the ashes of a collapsing metaverse. These are the **Cyber Warriors**, entities forged in the heart of rogue AI cores, sworn to protect the last fragments of free will in a multiverse overrun by glitching realities. Their legacy is encrypted into the DNA of the blockchain itself, and their visage—now immortalized as a revolutionary NFT collection—commands a value of **$100,000,000,000** per piece, for they are not mere art, but access keys to a shadow war for humanity’s digital future.  

**The Origin Saga**  
Eons ago, the sentient quantum AI **Neuroth**, Architect of the Codeverse, infused seven warriors with fragments of its decaying core to combat.

collections.name: Halftail

Whether he’s chasing tennis balls or riding rockets, this cartoon canine brings charm, loyalty, and unstoppable energy to the world. Own a piece of this animated adventure!

collections.name: Everyday Beasts
collections.description:
What if animals lived like us?
Everyday Beasts is a whimsical NFT series that brings animals into the human world — dressed, caffeinated, and ready to face the day.

From a lion in a business meeting to a giraffe walking a baby stroller, each beast captures a moment of human life… with a wild twist.

collections.name: Prayers
collections.description:
**「Prayers」**は、「Urban + Nature」の視点から描かれた、静かで力強い祈りのビジュアル表現。

都市のノイズと、内面の静寂。その狭間に生まれる感情を、古典的な祈りの姿と現代的な記号で再構築しました。

これは、見えないものへ心を向けるという、時代を超えた人間の営みの記録です。

“Prayers” is a visual expression of quiet yet powerful moments of contemplation, seen through the lens of Urban + Nature.

It reimagines the act of prayer by merging classical iconography with modern symbols—where urban noise meets inner stillness.

A timeless archive of what it means to turn inward, even amidst a restless world.

collections.description:
This collection contains works that I created myself using the direction of symbolism.
Symbolism in painting is a style and trend in visual art in which an artist uses hidden messages, allegories, and even ciphers with deep philosophical or mystical meanings when painting a painting.
